T08TD4148E:252b-0: @252b ` // bslab ba bcu'i cho ga bzhugs //
T08TD4148E:252b-3: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung nas byang chub snying po la mchis kyi bar du /
T08TD4148E:252b-4: rkang gnyis kyi mchog sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thams cad mkhyen zhing thams cad gzigs pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
T08TD4148E:253a-0: 'dod chags dang bral pa rnams kyi mchog chos la skyabs su @253a * //
T08TD4148E:253a-2: tshogs rnams kyi mchog dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
T08TD4148E:253a-3: de ltar lan gnyis lan gsum du'o zhes ba skyabs su 'gro ba'i cho ga'o //
T08TD4148E:253a-5: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste sang nyi ma shar gyi bar du srog gcod pa thams cad dang gzhan gyi nor 'phrog pa thams cad dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-6: mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-10: myos par 'gyur ba bag med pa'i gnas dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-11: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-18: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang pa las slar zlog par bgyi'o //
T08TD4148E:253a-19: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyi bslab pa la rjes su slob bo //
T08TD4148E:253a-21: sems kyi rgyan gyi phyir dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-22: sems kyi yo byad kyi phyir dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-23: don gyi mchog sangs rgyas nyid rab tu 'grub pa'i slad du /
T08TD4148E:253a-24: bdag gso sbyong la gnas par slob dpon gyis gzung du gsol /
T08TD4148E:253a-25: de ltar lan gnyis lan gsum du'o //
T08TD4148E:253a-26: bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-27: gso sbyong gi sdom pa'i cho ga'o //
T08TD4148E:253a-29: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung nas ji srid byang chub snying po la mchis kyi bar du /
T08TD4148E:253a-30: srog gcod pa spangs te sog gcod pa las bzlog par bgyi'o //
T08TD4148E:253a-32: ma byin par len pa dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-33: 'dod pas log par g-yem pa dang /
T08TD4148E:253a-40: log par lta ba las bzlog par bgyi'o //
T08TD4148E:253a-41: de ltar lan gnyis lan gsum du'o zhes pa bslab pa bcu'i cho ga klu sgrub kyi zhal snga nas gsungs pa rtse thang lo ts'a ba gzhon nu'i zhabs kyi 'gyur /
